        {
            "text": "Improved measurements will allow refinement of theory. ",
            "section": "II. hc STUDIES",
            "paragraph_rank": 6,
            "section_rank": 3
        },
        {
            "text": "BESIII is studying",
            "section": "II. hc STUDIES",
            "paragraph_rank": 6,
            "section_rank": 3
        },
        {
            "text": "Invariant mass distributions of the high energy gamma and V are shown in Fig. 1, where clear signals for \u03c7 c1 \u2192 \u03b3V are observed. ",
            "section": "II. hc STUDIES",
            "paragraph_rank": 7,
            "section_rank": 3,
            "ref_spans": [
                {
                    "start": 73,
                    "end": 79,
                    "type": "figure",
                    "ref_id": "fig_0",
                    "text": "Fig. 1"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "text": "Preliminary results are given in Table III and compared to CLEOc [12] and perturbative QCD predictions, [13] which for \u03c7 c1 \u2192 \u03b3V are an order of magnitude too low. ",
            "section": "II. hc STUDIES",
            "paragraph_rank": 7,
            "section_rank": 3,
            "ref_spans": [
                {
                    "start": 33,
